title: Snowbound Seduction - Helen Brooks
description: Sensible...but ripe for seduction! Sensible Rachel Ellington is used to being invisible to men, and that's fine. One run-in with male deceit in the past was enough to put her off for life! Now she's being pursued by millionaire businessman Zac Lawson - what could this dazzlingly handsome man see in her? It's with trepidation that Rachel accepts Zac's invitation to a Christmas country house party. And when they end up stranded by the wintry weather she suddenly knows exactly why she was so nervous...This is the perfect setting for slow, sweet seduction, though she's as pure as the driven snow!
